s%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Naga-majority%20Ukhrul%20district%20on%20October%2025%2C%20Raising%20%E2%80%93%20considered%20an%20ideologue%20of%20the%20NSCN%20%E2%80%93%20said%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20separate%20flag%20%E2%80%9Cis%20at%20the%20stage%20of%20finalisation%20while%20the%20matter%20concerning%20constitution%20is%20still%20under%20negotiation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2FMungchan-ZimikUkhrul-Oct-25-Senior-leader-of-the-NSCN-IM-and-member-of-the-collective-leadership-of-th.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESangai%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20%E2%80%9Casserted%20that%20the%20NSCN%20(I-M)%20is%20ready%20to%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20(with%20the%20Union%20government)%20in%20case%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Nagas%20is%20not%20honoured%20(by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20Raising%2C%20while%20reiterating%20that%20%E2%80%9CNagas%20are%20mission-oriented%20people%20and%20have%20no%20intention%20of%20merging%20with%20India%20or%20Myanmar%E2%80%9D%2C%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20Indian%20law%20shall%20bind%20us.%E2%80%9D%20Claiming%20that%20any%20form%20of%20%E2%80%9Cimposition%20(of%20the%20Centre)%20in%20the%20Naga%20region%20will%20make%20their%20movement%20more%20vibrant%20to%20defend%20their%20ancestral%20land%20rights%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20top%20NSCN%20leader%20who%20has%20been%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20peace%20talks%20with%20Centre%20since%202015%2C%20said%20New%20Delhi%20has%20%E2%80%9Crecognised%20the%20unique%20history%20of%20the%20Nagas%20after%20a%20series%20of%20political%20negotiations.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20stated%20in%20his%20address%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20will%20be%20no%20peace%20in%20the%20Indian%20sub-continent%20without%20resolving%20the%20Naga%20issue.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20a%20long%20deadlock%20in%20the%20peace%20talks%20due%20to%20the%20NSCN%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20compromise%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20separate%20flag%20and%20a%20constitution%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20resumed%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-naga-kuki-peace-talks-muivah-nscn-im%5C%22%3Ethis%20past%20August%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Prior%20to%20those%20talks%2C%20NSCN%E2%80%99s%20topmost%20leader%20Th.%20Muivah%20had%20also%20reiterated%20those%20demands%20in%20his%20%E2%80%98Naga%20Independence%20Day%E2%80%99%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20flag%20and%20the%20constitution%20are%20naturally%20inseparable%20from%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20a%20people.%20It%20is%20universally%20an%20accepted%20truth%20that%20flag%20and%20constitution%20are%20constituent%20parts%20of%20sovereignty.%20There%20is%20no%20ambiguity%20about%20it.%20The%20Indian%20leaders%20understand%20it%20too.%20They%20must%20take%20the%20stand%20to%20speak%20the%20truth%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20octogenarian%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fukhrultimes.com%2Ffull-speech-of-nscn-im-supremo-th-muivah-77th-naga-independence-day-celebration%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20August%2014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698399945000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11122010%2FEfZNZmZUcActHdO.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnscn-im-threatens-walk-peace-talks-separate-flag-constitution-demand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NSCN%20(I-M)%20leader%20R.H.%20Raising%20claimed%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20separate%20flag%20%E2%80%9Cis%20at%20the%20stage%20of%20finalisation%20while%20the%20matter%20concerning%20constitution%20is%20still%20under%20negotiation.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnscn-im-threatens-walk-peace-talks-separate-flag-constitution-demand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSponge%20Bombs%26quot%3B%3A%20Israel's%20New%20Secret%20Weapon%20To%20Block%20Hamas%20Tunnels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFighting%20in%20Gaza%20has%20entered%20day%2021%20after%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20surprise%20cross-border%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20killing%20about%201%2C400%20people.%20Since%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20bombarding%20Gaza%2C%20in%20which%20more%20than%207%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20has%20also%20mounted%20an%20incursion%20deeper%20into%20Gaza%20on%20Friday%20as%20it%20readies%20for%20a%20ground%20offensive%20against%20Hamas.%20However%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20the%20Israeli%20troops%20face%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-updates-hamas-tunnel-warfare-and-lessons-for-israel-from-vietnam-war-al-qaeda-gaza-war-gaza-war-live-gaza-tunnels-4493256%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextensive%20Hamas%20tunnel%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20group%20is%20said%20to%20have%20taken%20several%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20reportedly%20has%20different%20kinds%20of%20tunnels%20--%20hundreds%20of%20kilometres%20long%20and%20up%20to%2080%20metres%20deep%20--%20running%20beneath%20the%20sandy%20360-sq-km%20coastal%20strip%20and%20its%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESponge%20bombs%C2%A0create%20sudden%20explosion%20of%20foam%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20fight%20Hamas%20through%20its%20tunnel%20network%2C%20Israel%20is%20reportedly%20making%20%26quot%3Bsponge%20bombs%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20create%20a%20sudden%20explosion%20of%20foam%20that%20rapidly%20expands%20and%20then%20hardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20testing%20the%20chemical%20grenades%2C%20which%20contain%20no%20explosives%20but%20are%20used%20to%20seal%20off%20gaps%20or%20tunnel%20entrances%20from%20which%20Hamas%20operatives%20may%20emerge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20devices%20are%20said%20to%20be%20encased%20within%20a%20protective%20plastic%20container%20that%20has%20a%20metal%20barrier%20that%20divides%20two%20distinct%20liquids.%20When%20activated%2C%20these%20liquids%20merge%20and%20advance%20toward%20their%20intended%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20were%20seen%20deploying%20these%20devices%20during%20exercises%20in%20a%20mock%20tunnel%20system%20near%20the%20Gaza%20border%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20elite%20units%20tasked%20with%20going%20underground%20is%20Yahalom%2C%20specialist%20commandos%20from%20Israel's%20Combat%20Engineering%20Corps%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bweasels%26quot%3B%2C%20who%20specialise%20in%20finding%2C%20clearing%2C%20and%20destroying%20the%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Hamas%20built%20its%20tunnel%20network%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20was%20created%20in%20Gaza%20in%201987%20and%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-israel-hamas-war-hamas-tunnels-hamas-terror-tunnels-israels-tall-challenge-in-ground-offensive-plan-4478223%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20digging%20tunnels%20in%20the%20mid-1990s%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tunnel%20network%20is%20a%20key%20reason%20why%20Hamas%20is%20stronger%20in%20Gaza%20than%20in%20the%20Israeli-occupied%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETunneling%20became%20easier%20in%202005%20when%20Israel%20pulled%20its%20soldiers%20and%20settlers%20out%20of%20Gaza%2C%20and%20when%20Hamas%20won%20power%20in%20a%202006%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(With%20agency%20inputs)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698399840000%2C