ted%20arms%20and%20ammunition%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20he%20has%20links%20with%20Bambiha%20gang%20and%20also%20Khalistani%20terrorists.%20To%20probe%20the%20Khalistani%20connect%2C%20his%20house%20and%20known%20hideouts%20in%20India%20had%20recently%20been%20raided%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20reward%20of%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20has%20also%20been%20issued%20for%20information%20on%20the%20gangster%2C%20while%20Interpol%20has%20put%20out%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interpol.int%2Fen%2FHow-we-work%2FNotices%2FRed-Notices%2FView-Red-Notices%232023-61633%5C%22%3Ered%20corner%20notice%20against%20Kadian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20is%20a%20request%20to%20the%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20of%20Interpol's%20member%20countries%20to%20find%20and%20temporarily%20detain%20a%20person%20until%20extradition%2C%20surrender%2C%20or%20a%20similar%20legal%20process%20can%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Interpol%20issued%20a%20Red%20Notice%20to%20all%20member%20countries%20against%20gangster%20Himanshu%20alias%20Bhau%2C%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20living%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20currently%20working%20on%20a%20plan%20to%20take%20down%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20and%20establish%20their%20dominance%20in%20US%20and%20Canada%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20is%20currently%20in%20Ahmedabad%20jail%20on%20drug%20smuggling%20charges%20that%20are%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA).%20Bishnoi%20is%20also%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moosewala.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20recently%20made%20the%20headlines%20again%20when%20he%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Sukhdool%20Singh%20in%20Canada.%20Sukhdool%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Sukha%20Duneke%2C%20was%20killed%20in