address%20it%20and%20hopefully%20prevent%20such%20behavior%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Not%20communicating%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%3A%20Come%20to%20the%20bar%20being%20rowdy%20and%20unruly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20going%20to%20be%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20understand%20what's%20happening%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3ETell%20your%20bartender%20about%20your%20situation%2C%20like%20time%20constraints%20or%20who's%20paying%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20going%20to%20a%20bar%20in%20a%20big%20group%2C%20communicate%20with%20us%20and%20let%20us%20know%20what%20is%20happening.%20For%20example%2C%20who's%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20first%20round%20of%20drinks%2C%20who's%20next%2C%20and%20how%20many%20tabs%20do%20you%20want%20to%20start%3F%20This%20helps%20your%20bartender%20have%20more%20control%20over%20the%20situation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20waiting%20for%20a%20friend%20or%20just%20grabbing%20a%20quick%20drink%20before%20dinner%2C%20let%20us%20know%2C%20too%2C%20so%20we%20can%20serve%20you%20with%20the%20consideration%20of%20urgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBartenders%20are%20both%20problem%20solvers%20and%20peacemakers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20bartenders%2C%20we%20have%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20everything%20that%20is%20going%20on%20at%20the%20bar.%20You%20never%20know%20if%20someone%20has%20entered%20the%20bar%20already%20drunk%20%E2%80%94%20serving%20just%20one%20drink%20might%20push%20them%20over%20the%20edge.%20This%20makes%20it%20important%20for%20us%20to%20observe%20people's%20behaviors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20notice%20someone%20who%20appears%20more%20touchy%2C%20chatty%2C%20or%20angry%2C%20I'll%20put%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20in%20front%20of%20them%20to%20help%20them%20calm%20down%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20good%20bartender%20remembers%20faces.%20They%20may%20not%20remember%20the%20name%2C%20but%20espe