C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatthew%20Belloni%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20drew%20ire%20from%20analysts.%20(Aron%20also%20drew%20headlines%20that%20year%20for%20appearing%20to%20wear%20no%20pants%20during%20a%20Zoom%20call).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20Aron%2C%20who%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20would%20fall%20victim%20to%20another%20sort%20of%20villain.%20Charging%20documents%20describe%20in%20detail%20Blackwood's%20%26quot%3Bsophisticated%20and%20devious%26quot%3B%20catfishing%20scheme%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20went%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20started%20with%20that%20March%20text.%20It's%20unknown%20how%20Blackwood%20got%20Aron's%20phone%20number%2C%20but%20at%20the%20time%20she%20must%20have%20assumed%20he%20was%20wealthy.%20She'd%20read%20about%20him%20online%20and%20his%20well-documented%20selling%20spree%20of%20AMC%20stock%2C%20charging%20documents%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20discreet%20and%20sent%20the%20text%20from%20a%20voice%20over%20internet%20protocol%2C%20or%20VoIP%2C%20so%20it%20couldn't%20be%20traced.%20A%20lawyer%20for%20Blackwood%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20also%20smart%2C%20according%20to%20a%20sentencing%20memo%20written%20by%20her%20lawyers.%20She%20had%20been%20a%20straight-A%20student%20at%20Evander%20Childs%20High%20School%20in%20the%20Bronx%2C%20graduating%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20class%20of%202006%20and%20scoring%20well%20on%20her%20SATs%2C%20the%20memo%20said.%20But%20because%20of%20her%20immigration%20status%20%E2%80%94%20she%20arrived%20in%20the%20US%20illegally%20from%20Jamaica%20as%20a%20child%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0she%20had%20no%20options%20when%20it%20came%20to%20financing%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20worked%20a%20number%20of%20odd%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20at%20a%20day%20care%20and%20as%20a%20nanny%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0all%20off%20the%20books%2C%20her%20lawyers%20said.%20But%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20she%20tried%20two%20new%20pursuits%3A%20day-trading%20and%20posing%20as%20a%20minor%20to%20try%20to%20lure%20men%20into%20seemingly%20illegal%20sexual%20conversations.%20Blackwood's%20lawyers%20said%20the%20latter%20pursuit%20was%20a%20result%20of%20unspecified%20mental%20and%20physical%20abuse%20against%20her%20by%20someone%20close%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20%26quot%3Bresentment%20toward%20her%20abusers%26quot%3B%20may%20have%20led%20her%20to%20text%20Aron%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wealthy%2C%20powerful%20man%20in%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20her%20lawyers%20said.%20(Though%20the%20indictment%20said%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20not%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%26quot%3B%20of%20Aron%20having%20a%20history%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20or%20harassment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20could%20have%20easily%20gone%20unanswered%20%E2%80%94%20had%20it%20not%20been%20for%20Blackwood's%20choice%20of%20name%3A%20Mia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAron%20recognized%20the%20name%2C%20linking%20her%20to%20a%20ballet%20dancer%20who%20had%20done%20%26quot%3Bunmentionable%20things%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20in%20his%20words%2C%20over%20text%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0to%20him%20just%20a%20few%20years%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSend%20me%20a%20naughty%20picture%2C%26quot%3B%20Blackwood%20texted%2C%20a%20couple%20weeks%20into%20their%20flirty%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20complied%2C%20sending%20some%20photos%20of%20himself%20solo%20and%20with%20another%20woman.%20When%20he%20asked%20for%20photos%20in%20return%2C%20Blackwood%20sent%20him%20images%20of%20an%20unnamed%20Russian%20model%20that%20she%20pulled%20from%20Instagram.%20Aron%20seemed%20to%20either%20not%20notice%20or%20not%20care%20that%20the%20woman%20in%20the%20pictures%20was%20not%20his%20ballerina%20paramour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EBlackwood%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20fake%20identities%2C%20and%20Mia%20is%20one%20of%20many%20she's%20assumed%20over%20the%20years.%20Law%20enforcement%20found%20at%20least%20five%20forms%20of%2