ictures%20and%20spread%20a%20false%20rumor%20that%20Aron%20had%20been%20intimate%20with%20a%20minor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20Aron%20realized%20he'd%20been%20caught%20up%20in%20some%20kind%20of%20trouble%2C%20and%20that%20he'd%20never%20actually%20met%20Mia.%20He%20consulted%20an%20attorney.%20The%20the%20next%20day%2C%20Blackwood%2C%20posing%20as%20Brian%2C%20threatened%20to%20text%20AMC%20board%20members%20the%20illicit%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOffers%20are%20coming%20in%20like%20crazy%20ppl%20love%20a%20scandal%2C%26quot%3B%20Blackwood%20wrote%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20Brian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20a%20separate%20line%2C%20Blackwood%20posed%20as%20Mia%20and%20discouraged%20Aron%20from%20hiring%20legal%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20could%20do%20more%20damage%20than%20you%20could%20while%20getting%20paid%20for%20doing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Brian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20Blackwood%20introduced%20a%20third%20fake%20identity%3A%20the%20representative%20of%20a%20media%20agency%2C%20who%20claimed%20they'd%20gotten%20a%20tip%20on%20Aron.%20It%20%26quot%3Bpromised%20to%20be%20damning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20Blackwood%20began%20to%20work%20the%20phone%20as%20all%20three%20of%20her%20characters%20and%20tried%20to%20lock%20down%20a%20payout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20%26quot%3Bmedia%20contact%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20informed%20Aron%20that%20an%20outlet%20would%20be%20buying%20the%20photos%20for%20%24250%2C000.%20As%20Mia%2C%20she%20suggested%20Aron%20inform%20his%20family%2C%20because%20Brian%20was%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20for%20the%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bsmart%20move%20was%20u%20should've%20been%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20texted%2C%20posing%20as%20Brian%20%E2%80%94%20and%20added%20that%20a%20bidding%20war%20had%20sent%20the%20price%20of%20the%20Aron%20scoop%20to%20%24315%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20just%20nine%20days%