etflix-disney-raise-subscription-prices-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Rath%20Prabhari%E2%80%99%20Move%20Illegal%20As%20It%20Is%20Wholesale%20Politicisation%20of%20Civil%20Services%3A%20EAS%20Sarma%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27134749%2FPM_Narendra_Modi_addressing_IAS_Probationers.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20IAS%20officer%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20deploy%20civil%20servants%20as%20%E2%80%9CRath%20Prabharis%E2%80%9D%20in%20election-bound%20states%20may%20provide%20temporary%20relief%2C%20but%20highlighted%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20intentions%20to%20use%20these%20officers%20to%20promote%20its%20achievements%20are%20%E2%80%9Cundesirable%20and%20illegal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20clarify%20that%20deploying%20civil%20servants%20as%20Rath%20Prabharis%20in%20poll-bound%20States%20violates%20the%20election%20laws%2C%20deploying%20civil%20servants%20at%20any%20level%2C%20anywhere%20else%2C%20at%20any%20time%2C%20is%20also%20undesirable%20and%20illegal%2C%20as%20it%20amounts%20to%20engaging%20civil%20servants%20in%20campaigning%20for%20a%20particular%20political%20party%20and%20wholesale%20politicisation%20of%20civil%20services%20in%20general%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarma%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20secretary%20Rajiv%20Gauba.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2017%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%5C%22%3Esent%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20all%20ministries%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20nominate%20officers%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20joint%20secretaries%2C%20directors%20and%20deputy%20secretaries%20in%20all%20the%20765%20districts%20of%20the%20country%20to%20deploy%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdistrict%20rath%20prabharis%20(special%20officers)%E2%80%9D%20between%20November%2020%2C%202023%20and%20January%2025%2C%202024%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshowcase%2Fcelebrate%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20last%20nine%20years%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2026%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpushback-forces-modi-govt-to-climb-down-on-calling-ias-officers-rath-prabharis%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20notice%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20that%20these%20activities%20should%20not%20be%20undertaken%20in%20the%20five%20states%20where%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20is%20in%20force%2C%20until%20December%205%2C%20for%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESarma%2C%20who%20had%20written%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20about%20the%20longer-term%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20politicisation%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20and%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign%2C%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccosy%20truce%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20ECI%20would%20only%20provide%20temporary%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20move%20%E2%80%9Cis%20only%20a%20half%20measure%2C%20as%20it%20merely%20provides%20a%20palliative%20to%20a%20far%20more%20serious%20malaise%20that%20seems%20to%20have%20already%20afflicted%20and%20spread%20fast%20in%20the%20body%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%20to%20Gauba%2C%20the%20former%20IAS%20officer%20said%20that%20the%20campaign%20will%20cause%20%E2%80%9Cirreversible%20damage%20%E2%80%A6%20to%20the%20role%20and%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20and%20the%20irreparable%20damage%20it%20will%20cause%20to%20the%20political%20neutrality%20of%20the%20civil%20services%2C%20that%20is%20implicit%20in%20Part%20XIV%20of%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECivil%20services%2C%20like%20any%20other%20wing%20of%20the%20government%2C%20owe%20their%20existence%20to%20the%20constitution%20and%20their%20allegiance%20can%20only%20be%20to%20the%20constitution%20and%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20not%20to%20an%20individual%20or%20a%20particular%20political%20party%2C%20Sarma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20raised%20some%20crucial%20questions%20about%20the%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign%2C%20such%20as%20why%20civil%20servants%20are%20expected%20to%20highlight%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20government%20during%20the%20last%20%E2%80%9Cnine%20years%E2%80%9D%20alone%3B%20and%20why%20civil%20servants%20should%20be%20forced%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshowcase%2F%20celebrate%E2%80%9D%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20NDA%20government%2C%20when%20the%20Constitution%20envisages%20them%20to%20be%20a%20politically%20neutral%20instrument%20of%20continuing%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESarma%20also%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Csymptoms%20of%20politicisation%20of%20the%20civil%20services%E2%80%9D%20are%20already%20visible%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cundue%20extensions%E2%80%9D%20granted%20by%20the%20political%20executive%20to%20those%20who%20head%20Central%20investigation%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20long%20term%2C%20politicisation%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20is%20not%20desirable%20either%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20or%20for%20the%20political%20executive.%20Sooner%20they%20realise%20it%2C%20the%20better%20it%20is%20for%20either%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20asking%20Gauba%20to%20%E2%80%9Cappreciate%20the%20wider%20implications%20of%20moves%20such%20as%20the%20ongoing%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign%20for%20the%20future%20of%20civil%20services%20in%20India%20and%20for%20the%20well-being%20of%20our%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20letter%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%20Former%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShri%20Rajiv%20Gauba%3Cbr%3E%20Union%20Cabinet%20Secretary%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDear%20Shri%20Gauba%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20must%20have%20closely%20followed%20the%20concerns%20expressed%20by%20some%20of%20us%20about%20the%20prudence%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Central%20government%20to%20engage%20senior%20officers%20as%20%E2%80%9CDistrict%20Rath%20Prabharis%E2%80%9D%20under%20their%20purview%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshowcase%2Fcelebrate%20achievements%20of%20the%20NDA%20government%20during%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20through%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20from%2020th%20November%202023%20to%2025th%20January%202024%E2%80%B3.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApparently%2C%20after%20a%20public%20outcry%20and%20complaints%20before%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%2C%20the%20ECI%20and%20those%20in%20the%20government%20seem%20to%20have%20arrived%20at%20a%20cosy%2C%20truce%20not%20to%20extend%20the%20campaign%20to%20those%20States%20where%20Assembly%20elections%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20shortly%20(https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpushback-forces-modi-govt-to-climb-down-on-calling-ias-officers-rath-prabharis)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20may%20at%20best%20be%20a%20temporary%20relief%20for%20civil%20servants%2C%20it%20is%20only%20a%20half%20measure%2C%20as%20it%20merely%20provides%20a%20palliative%20to%20a%20far%20more%20serious%20malaise%20that%20seems%20to%20have%20already%20afflicted%20and%20spread%20fast%20in%20the%20body%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20in%20India.%20Let%20me%20clarify%20that%20deploying%20civil%20servants%20as%20Rath%20Prabharis%20in%20poll-bound%20States%20violates%20the%20election%20laws%2C%20deploying%20civil%20servants%20at%20any%20level%2C%20anywhere%20else%2C%20at%20any%20time%2C%20is%20also%20undesirable%20and%20illegal%2C%20as%20it%20amounts%20to%20engaging%20civil%20servants%20in%20campaigning%20for%20a%20particular%20political%20party%20and%20wholesale%20politicisation%20of%20civil%20services%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20connection%2C%20I%20invite%20your%20attention%20to%20a%20letter%20addressed%20on%20the%20subject%20to%20Rashtrapatiji%20by%20Prof.%20Jagdeep%20S.%20Chhokar%2C%20Former%20Dean%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%2C%20Ahmedabad%20(IIM-A)%20and%20myself%2C%20raising%20longer-term%20concerns%20about%20politicisation%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20and%20the%20Constitutional%20implications%20of%20the%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20copy%20of%20that%20letter%20was%20sent%20to%20you%2C%20the%20same%20may%20also%20be%20accessed%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20at%20https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2023%2F10%2Fopen-letter-to-president-of-india-regarding-ruling-party-using-its-power-to-influence-elections%2F.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20would%20request%20you%20to%20examine%20each%20one%20of%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20us%20in%20that%20letter%20carefully%2C%20as%20they%20not%20only%20relate%20to%20the%20illegalities%20arising%20in%20the%20immediate%20context%20of%20the%20ensuing%20Assembly%20elections%20but%20also%20relate%20to%20the%20likely%20adverse%20impact%20of%20the%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign%20on%20the%202024%20Parliament%20elections%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20irreversible%20damage%20that%20such%20a%20campaign%20will%20cause%20to%20the%20role%20and%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20and%20the%20irreparable%20damage%20it%20will%20cause%20to%20the%20political%20neutrality%20of%20the%20civil%20services%2C%20that%20is%20implicit%20in%20Part%20XIV%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20pointed%20out%20by%20us%20in%20our%20letter%2C%20it%20was%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20who%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20in%20India.%20While%20addressing%20trainee%20civil%20servants%20on%20April%2021%2C%201947%2C%20he%20emphasised%20that%20they%20should%20%E2%80%9Cmaintain%20the%20utmost%20impartiality%20and%20incorruptibility%20of%20administration.%20A%20civil%20servant%20cannot%20afford%20to%2C%20and%20must%20not%2C%20take%20part%20in%20politics%E2%80%9D%20It%20was%20on%20that%20basis%20that%20the%20civil%20services%20conduct%20rules%20were%20framed%20by%20the%20government.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20ill-conceived%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign%20involving%20civil%20servants%20makes%20a%20mockery%20of%20Sardar%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20services%2C%20like%20any%20other%20wing%20of%20the%20government%2C%20owes%20its%20existence%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20As%20an%20instrument%20provided%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20seamless%20time-wise%2C%20and%20politically%20neutral.%20Its%20allegiance%20is%20and%20should%20be%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20not%20to%20an%20individual%20or%20a%20particular%20political%20party.%20It%20is%20bound%20by%20the%20democratic%20values%20implicit%20in%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20specific%20reference%20to%20the%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign%2C%20the%20crucial%20questions%20that%20arise%20are%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EConsidering%20that%20the%20campaign%20engages%20civil%20servants%2C%20why%20should%20it%20be%20confined%20to%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20government%20during%20the%20last%20%E2%80%9Cnine%20years%E2%80%9D%20alone%3F%20Why%20should%20it%20not%20cover%20the%20achievements%20during%20the%20last%20seven%20and%20a%20half%20decades%20of%20independent%20India%20when%20the%20country%20made%20progress%20in%20leaps%20and%20bounds%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIf%20it%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9CRath%20Prabhari%E2%80%9D%20campaign%20in%20which%20civil%20servants%20are%20to%20be%20engaged%2C%20whose%20%E2%80%9CRath%E2%80%9D%20is%20it%3F%20Does%20it%20belong%20exclusively%20to%20the%20NDA%20government%20or%20the%20system%20of%20a%20seamless%20governance%20system%20that%20the%20Constitution%20has%20provided%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EWhy%20should%20civil%20servants%20be%20forced%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshowcase%2F%20celebrate%E2%80%9D%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20NDA%20government%2C%20when%20the%20Constitution%20envisages%20them%20to%20be%20a%20politically%20neutral%20instrument%20of%20continuing%20governance%3F%20The%20responsibility%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20is%20to%20administer%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20government%20to%20the%20extent%20they%20remain%20consistent%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20not%20%E2%80%9Ccelebrate%E2%80%9D%20their%20implementation.%20Celebrations%20should%20lie%20exclusively%20within%20the%20domain%20of%20the%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Cp%3EConsidering%20that%20the%20idea%20underlying%20the%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign%20exclusively%20revolves%20around%20the%20NDA%20government%E2%80%99s%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cachievements%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20inevitably%2C%20it%20has%20a%20political%20connotation.%20Irrespective%20of%20the%20limited%20perspective%20of%20its%20implications%20for%20the%20ensuing%20Assembly%20and%20the%202024%20Parliament%20elections%2C%20there%20are%20far%20more%20serious%20implications%20with%20reference%20to%20the%20laws%20that%20govern%20both%20politicians%20and%20civil%20servants.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20pointed%20out%20in%20our%20letter%20cited%2C%20under%20Section%20171C%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhoever%20voluntarily%20interferes%20or%20attempts%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20free%20exercise%20of%20any%20electoral%20right%20commits%20the%20offence%20of%20undue%20influence%20at%20an%20election%E2%80%9C.%20For%20any%20public%20authority%2C%20including%20the%20political%20executive%2C%20to%20coerce%20public%20servants%20into%20such%20an%20activity%20is%20therefore%20punishable%20not%20only%20under%20the%20relevant%20election%20laws%20but%20also%20under%20the%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20Rule%205(1)%20of%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Conduct%20Rules%2C%201964%2C%20and%20the%20corresponding%20provisions%20of%20the%20Conduct%20Rules%20applicable%20to%20the%20All%20India%20Services%2C%20the%20Audit%20and%20Accounts%20Service%20and%20the%20other%20services%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Personnel%20communication%20File%20No.%20I-28047%2F08%2F2023-coord%20dated%2017-10-2023%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20Government%20servant%20shall%20be%20a%20member%20of%2C%20or%20be%20otherwise%20associated%20with%2C%20any%20political%20party%20or%20any%20organisation%20which%20takes%20part%20in%20politics%20nor%20shall%20he%20take%20part%20in%2C%20subscribe%20in%20aid%20of%2C%20or%20assist%20in%20any%20other%20manner%2C%20any%20political%20movement%20or%20activity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEngaging%20members%20of%20any%20of%20the%20central%20civil%20services%20in%20the%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign%2C%20which%20is%20clearly%20political%20in%20nature%2C%20would%20therefore%20infringe%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Conduct%20Rule.%20All%20those%20public%20functionaries%20including%20senior%20civil%20servants%20who%20become%20a%20party%20to%20engaging%20other%20civil%20servants%20in%20this%20campaign%20would%20also%20be%20responsible%20for%20violating%20those%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20concerned%20about%20the%20symptoms%20of%20politicisation%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20already%20visible%20all%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20distressing%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20find%20undue%20extensions%20granted%20by%20the%20political%20executive%20to%20those%20who%20head%20crucial%20institutions%20involved%20in%20governance%2C%20including%20the%20Central%20investigation%20agencies%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20compromise%20their%20political%20neutrality%20and%20their%20overall%20effectiveness.%20For%20the%20civil%20services%20to%20be%20effective%20and%20credible%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20invoke%20public%20trust%2C%20they%20should%20remain%20apolitical%20and%20resist%20any%20attempt%20to%20politicise%20their%20rank%20and%20file.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20long%20term%2C%20politicisation%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20is%20not%20desirable%20either%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20or%20for%20the%20political%20executive.%20Sooner%20they%20realise%20it%2C%20the%20better%20it%20is%20for%20either%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20head%20of%20civil%20services%2C%20I%20would%20urge%20you%20to%20appreciate%20the%20wider%20implications%20of%20moves%20such%20as%20the%20ongoing%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign%20for%20the%20future%20of%20civil%20services%20in%20India%20and%20for%20the%20well-being%20of%20our%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20sincerely%20hope%20that%20you%20will%20consider%20each%20one%20of%20the%20concerns%20expressed%20by%20us%20in%20our%20appeal%20to%20the%20President%20of%20India%20and%20act%20decisively%2C%20and%20unhesitatingly%2C%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20long-term%20interest%20of%20our%20democracy.%20Failure%20to%20do%20so%20would%20amount%20not%20only%20to%20damaging%20the%20political%20neutrality%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20that%20the%20Constitution%20envisages%20but%20also%20to%20damaging%20the%20very%20fabric%20of%20our%20hard-earned%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERegards%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYours%20sincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%20Visakhapatnam%3Cbr%3E%2027-10-2023%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698396329000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27134749%2FPM_Narendra_Modi_addressing_IAS_Probationers.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frath-prabhari-illegal-wholesale-politicisation-civil-services-eas-sarma%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20IAS%20officer%20said%20that%20the%20'truce'%20between%20the%20ECI%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20not%20deploy%20'Rath%20Prabharis'%20in%20election-bound%20states%20does%20not%20address%20the%20%26quot%3Bserious%20malaise%20that%20seems%20to%20have%20already%20afflicted%20and%20