ods%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Government%20Defends%20NCERT%20Modules%20Crediting%20Modi%20With%20Chandrayaan-3%20Success%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18105527%2FF8pgm08bQAA7BaK.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20government%20has%20defended%20National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%E2%80%99s%20(NCERT%E2%80%99s)%20reference%20to%20mythology%20in%20its%20account%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20and%20the%20attribution%20of%20the%20mission%E2%80%99s%20success%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20the%20supplementary%20reading%20material%20published%20last%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reading%20material%20that%20was%20launched%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20ISRO%20chief%20S.%20Somanath%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fncert-reading-modules-credit-modi-for-success-of-chandrayaan-3-mix-space-science-with-vedas%5C%22%3Eexhaustively%20quotes%20the%20prime%20minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20emphasises%20on%20the%20role%20of%20mythology%20while%20referring%20to%20India%20as%20Bharat%20in%20the%20text.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fmoon-and-flying-chariots-government-defends-mythology-and-narendra-modi-in-science-texts%2Fcid%2F1975578%5C%22%3Ethe%20government%20said%20that%20mythology%20provides%20ideas%20that%20lead%20to%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20new%20knowledge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNumerous%20research%20studies%20emphasise%20that%20mythology%20plays%20an%20indispensable%20role%20in%20the%20cultural%20fabric%20of%20any%20country%2C%20including%20Bharat.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20integration%20of%20culture%20into%20education%20not%20only%20fosters%20a%20profound%20un