al%20agencies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fed-arrests-west-bengal-forest-minister-trinamool-leader-jyotipriya-mallick-ration-scam%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Dravidian%20Model%20and%20Its%20Long%20History%20of%20Upholding%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Rights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27125848%2FF8aZDeDWsAA8BFe.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EInflection%20point%20is%20a%20term%20that%20signifies%20a%20moment%20of%20transformation.%20It%20is%20a%20point%20where%20the%20painful%20stasis%20gives%20way%20to%20a%20new%20trajectory.%20The%20One%20Hundred%20and%20Sixth%20Amendment%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20was%20passed%20by%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20September%2020%20amidst%20fanfare%2C%20with%20the%20spin%20doctors%20for%20manufacturing%20consent%20working%20overtime%20to%20attribute%20the%20historical%20significance%20of%20legislating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-date-set-for-implementation-as-womens-reservation-bill-is-passed-unanimously-by-rajya-sabha%5C%22%3Ewomen%E2%80%99s%20reservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20legislative%20bodies%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20immediately%20became%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20wanted%20to%20earn%20brownie%20points%20among%20aspiring%20women%20by%20pointing%20to%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20while%20making%20sure%20that%2C%20by%20design%2C%20the%20Act%20is%20not%20implemented%20immediately.%20Since%20it%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20much-delayed%20decadal%20census%20and%20a%20future%20delimitation%20exercise%20with%20an%20indeterminate%20timeline%2C%20it%20not%20only%20has%20no%20date%20of%20arrival%20but%20also%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20disturb%20the%20fragile%20federal%20structure%20of%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20anguish%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20cynical%20politicking%20induced%20among%20women%20who%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20decades%20for%20the%20change%2C%20is%20still%20an%20undercurrent%2C%20as%20we%20speak.%20The%20Kalaignar%20Centenary%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Rights%20Conference%20ideated%20by%20DMK%20deputy%20secretary%20Kanimozhi%20Karunanidhi%20and%20organised%20by%20the%20DMK%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Wing%20on%20October%2014%2C%202023%20in%20Chennai%20brought%20together%20voices%20from%20across%20India%20that%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20intentional%20delay%20in%20implementing%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20in%20addition%20to%20pointing%20at%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20political%20mainstreaming%20of%20the%20core%20ideas%20of%20Dravidian%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%2C%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%2C%20the%20alliance%20partners%20have%20met%20thrice%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Patna%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20representatives%20of%20constituent%20parties%20have%20addressed%20the%20public%20together%20in%20a%20public%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20leaders%20from%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20CPI%2C%20CPM%2C%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(U)%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20People%E2%80%99s%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20addressed%20the%20gathering%2C%20who%20were%20largely%20women%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20leaders%20in%20their%20speeches%20delivered%20in%20Tamil%2C%20English%20and%20Hindi%2C%20not%20only%20reflected%20on%20the%20social%20justice%20history%20of%20their%20parties%20and%20the%20land%20they%20belong%20to%20but%20also%20paid%20rich%20accolades%20to%20the%20Dravidian%20movement%20and%20Kalaignar%20Karunanidhi%E2%80%99s%20foresight%2C%20progressiveness%20and%20politics%20of%20self-respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHistory%20of%20emancipatory%20conferences%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Dravidian%20movement%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Women%20Rights%20Conference%20by%20a%20mainstream%20political%20party%20in%20electoral%20politics%20is%20viewed%20as%20an%20outlier%20by%20political%20observers%2C%20it%20is%20not%20new%20for%20the%20Dravidian%20movement%20which%20has%20seen%20conferences%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20issues%20right%20from%20the%20historic%201929%20Self%20Respect%20Conference.%20It%20was%20the%20resolutions%20declared%20in%20this%20conference%20that%20served%20as%20inspirations%20for%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20(Tamil%20Nadu)%20(Amendment)%20Act%201967%2C%20which%20legalised%20priestless%20self-respect%20Hindu%20marriages%20and%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20(Tamil%20Nadu%20Amendment)%20Act%2C%201989%2C%20bestowing%20women%20equal%20rights%20to%20succession.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20that%2C%20the%20conference%20also%20proposed%20a%20resolution%20to%20make%2016%20the%20age%20of%20marriage%20for%20girls%3B%20that%20a%20husband%20and%20wife%20should%20be%20able%20to%20separate%20legally%20in%20case%20of%20marital%20incompatibility%3B%20to%20reject%20inequality%20by%20birth%2C%20that%20is%2C%20Varnashrama%20Dharma%3B%20that%20every%20eligible%20girl%20child%20must%20get%20primary%20education%20with%20public%20funds%3B%20and%20that%20women%20should%20be%20employed%20greatly%20as%20primary%20education%20teachers.%20Also%2C%20it%20was%20during%20the%201938%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Conference%20at%20Chennai%2C%20that%20E.V.%20Ramaswamy%20was%20bestowed%20with%20the%20title%20%E2%80%98Periyar%E2%80%99%2C%20by%20leading%20women%20leaders%20of%20those%20times%2C%20Annai%20Meenambal%20Sivaraj%2C%20Neelambigai%20Ammaiyar%2C%20Dharmambal%20Ammaiyar%20and%20Moovalur%20Ramamirtham%20Ammaiyar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20a%20resolution%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20DMK%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Wing%20conference%20in%20Cuddalore%20for%2033%25%20reservation%20in%20legislative%20bodies%2C%20as%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20long-standing%20support%20that%20the%20party%20extended%20to%20this%20critical%20policy%20of%20women%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27125834%2FF8as6Exb0AANzkH.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221186%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27125834%2FF8as6Exb0AANzkH.jpeg%201186w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27125834%2FF8as6Exb0AANzkH-300x158.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27125834%2FF8as6Exb0AANzkH-1024x540.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682007%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDMK%20MP%20Kanimozhi%20speaks%20at%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20conference%20in%20Chennai%20on%20October%2014%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40KanimozhiDMK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMainstreaming%20of%20the%20Dravidian%20Model%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20core%20message%20of%20this%20conference%20was%20put%20forth%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20M.K.%20Stalin%3A%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20be%20able%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20a%20message%20that%20was%20reiterated%20by%20the%20other%20leaders.%20But%20the%20emergent%20common%20theme%20of%20the%20speeches%20was%20the%20unequivocal%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Dravidian%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20Periyar%2C%20C.N.%20Annadurai%20and%20Kalaignar%20Karunanidhi%20%E2%80%93%20in%20enriching%20the%20social%20justice%20conversation%20and%20action%20in%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20%E2%80%98Self%20Respect%E2%80%99%20being%20the%20bedrock%20on%20which%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20Dravidian%20Movement%20are%20built%2C%20it%20was%20no%20wonder%20that%20the%20DMK%20advocated%20for%20the%20preservation%20and%20enrichment%20of%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20states.%20When%20Kalaignar%20Karunanidhi%2C%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20a%20three-member%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20former%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Madras%20high%20court%20P.V.%20Rajamannar%20was%20set%20up%20to%20study%20the%20Centre-State%20relations%20and%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20committee%20were%20the%20abolition%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Services%2C%20constitution%20of%20an%20inter-state%20council%2C%20abolition%20of%20governor%20office%2C%20among%20others.%20The%20championing%20of%20state%20rights%2C%20while%20now%20caricatured%20as%20a%20uniquely%20southern%20phenomenon%2C%20saw%20the%20emergence%20of%20an%20array%20of%20voices%20from%20across%20India%20in%20the%201970s%20and%2080s%2C%20like%20Jyoti%20Basu%2C%20Biju%20Patnaik%2C%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20N.T.%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20historic%20Anandpur%20Sahib%20Resolution%20of%201973%20and%20the%20Srinagar%20Resolution%20of%201983.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20conference%20saw%20Dimple%20Yadav%2C%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%2C%20mention%20the%20Rajamannar%20Committee%2C%20essentially%20bringing%20the%20document%20to%20the%20fore%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Centre-state%20relationship%20cannot%20be%20more%20skewed.%20It%20is%20a%20significant%20undercurrent%20that%20we%20are%20now%20witnessing%20where%20states%20across%20India%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20rearrange%20the%20Centre-state%20relationship%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20self-respect.%20Along%20those%20lines%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20NCP%20MP%2C%20highlighted%20how%20%E2%80%98cooperative%20federalism%E2%80%99%20is%20under%20threat%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20conference%20saw%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20calling%20for%20the%20rejection%20of%20any%20system%20%E2%80%93%20societal%2C%20religious%20or%20political%20%E2%80%93%20which%20thrives%20on%20the%20oppression%20of%20women%20and%20forces%20us%20to%20collude%20with%20it%20and%20highlighted%20the%20urgency%20with%20which%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20in%20legislative%20bodies%20needs%20to%20be%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20long-standing%20demand%20for%20caste%20census%20gaining%20support%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20the%20dire%20need%20for%20rational%20intervention%20towards%20addressing%20systemic%20backwardness%2C%20the%20voices%20from%20this%20conference%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20Leshi%20Singh%20of%20Janata%20Dal%20(U)%20%E2%80%93%20added%20weight%20to%20this%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20voices%20in%20this%20conference%20were%20also%20reflective%20of%20the%20extraordinary%20circumstances%20that%20are%20felt%20by%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%2C%20especially%20women%2C%20who%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20lacklustre%20macroeconomic%20situation%20in%20their%20homes%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20due%20to%20the%20impacts%20of%20demonetisation%20and%20the%20inflationary%20pressures%20due%20to%20faulty%20GST%20implementation.%20While%20families%20across%20India%20are%20increasingly%20seeing%20their%20life%20savings%20erode%20and%20accumulating%20debt%20burden%20due%20to%20the%20economic%20policies%20of%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20intervene%20and%20support%20their%20residents%20is%20hampered%20by%20the%20loss%20of%20fiscal%20freedom%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20creeping%20encroachment%20of%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20states%20to%20raise%20revenue.%20The%20urge%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20centralise%20decision-making%20coupled%20with%20the%20interventions%20in%20non-BJP%20ruled%20states%20through%20the%20office%20of%20the%20governor%20is%20stymieing%20the%20states%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20undertake%20individual%20development%20journeys.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20economy%20is%20in%20a%20poor%20state%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20is%20engaging%20in%20a%20PR%20blitzkrieg%20proclaiming%20an%20era%20of%20abundance%2C%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%2C%20while%20muzzling%20the%20independent%20media%20and%20interfering%20with%20institutions%20which%20are%20in%20charge%20of%20measuring%20the%20economic%20and%20societal%20status%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20women%20of%20this%20country%20can%20no%20longer%20take%20the%20spectacular%20ineptness%20with%20which%20this%20country%20is%20ruled%2C%20alongside%20the%20tendency%20of%20the%20ruling%20disposition%20to%20engage%20in%20perception%20management%20by%20using%20religion%20and%20exclusionary%20patriotism.%20The%20swiftness%20with%20which%20the%20ruling%20disposition%20and%20their%20right-wing%20media%20ecosystem%20responded%20to%20the%20Gaza%20issue%20to%20peddle%20a%20convenient%20political%20narrative%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20wanton%20silence%20as%20a%20response%20to%20inhumane%20violations%20in%20Manipur%20along%20sectarian%20lines%20over%20several%20weeks%20is%20revelatory%20of%20their%20ineptness%20and%20bigotry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20states%20across%20India%20have%20intentions%20and%20matching%20actions%20to%20empower%20women%20in%20a%20true%20sense%20as%20against%20tokenism%20measures%20that%20the%20ruling%20disposition%20at%20the%20Centre%20is%20fond%20of.%20The%20use%20of%20religion%20for%20political%20means%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20organisational%20ecosystem%20is%20endangering%20the%20decades-long%20improvements%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%20which%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20persistent%20efforts%20via%20legislative%2C%20social%20and%20economic%20interventions.%20The%20women%20of%20this%20country%2C%20especially%20from%20backward%20and%20oppressed%20sections%2C%20want%20a%20better%20deal%2C%20a%20way%20for%20them%20to%20leap%20across%20millennia-long%20subjugation%20and%20neglect.%20The%20Dravidian%20model%20strongly%20supports%20the%20all-around%20empowerment%20of%20women%20and%20views%20the%2033%25%20reservation%20as%20the%20key%20block%20in%20the%20puzzle%20to%20unleash%20the%20intellectual%20and%20material%20potential%20of%20half%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Kanimozhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPolitics%20should%20be%20determined%2C%20defined%20and%20decided%20with%20opinions%2C%20concerns%20and%20aspirations%20of%20women.%20There%20should%20be%20no%20politics%2C%20no%20policy-making%2C%20and%20no%20governance%20without%20listening%20to%20what%20we%20want%20to%20say.%20Let%20us%20come%20together.%20Let%20us%20rewrite%20history%20and%20make%20sure%20there%20is%20justice.%20Justice%20not%20just%20for%20the%20women%20of%20this%20country%20but%20justice%20for%20everybody%2C%20every%20human%20being%20in%20this%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYazhini%20P.M%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20her%20post-graduation%20and%20is%20the%20spokesperson%20and%20social%20media%20coordinator%20of%20the%20DMK%20women%E2%80%99s%20wing.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698392706000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27125848%2FF8aZDeDWsAA8BFe.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdravidian-model-womens-rights-conference-dmk%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20women's%20rights%20conference%20held%20by%20the%20DMK%20in%20Chennai%20highlighted%20the%20challenges%20that%20women%20face%20today%20and%20how%20social%20justice%20politics%20can%20help%20overcome%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdravidian-model-womens-rights-conference-dmk%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%2C%20Rizwan...%3A%20Best%20XI%20Of%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20At%20Halfway%20Stage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20is%20past%20the%20halfway%20mark%20in%20the%20league%20stages.%20The%20league%20stage%2C%20which%20consists%20of%2045%20matches%2C%20has%20completed%2023%20matches%20as%20of%20October%2024%20and%20has%20seen%20some%20sparkling%20cricketing%20action%20across%20multiple%20venues.%20Hosts%20India%20are%20the%20only%20team%20without%20a%20defeat%2C%20while%20every%20other%20team%20has%20picked%20up%20at%20least%20one%20win.%20Defending%20champions%20England%20are%20struggling%20to%20make%20their%20mark%2C%20with%20one%20win%20in%20four%20matches%2C%20while%20Afghanistan%20are%20on%20the%20surge%2C%20with%20two%20wins%20against%20two%20former%20world%20champions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20individual%20performances%20in%20the%20tournament%20have%20been%20a%20sight%20to%20behold%2C%20which%20are%20driving%20teams%20on%20the%20path%20to%20the%20most%20coveted%20trophy%20in%20cricket.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20best%20XI%20of%20players%20at%20the%20ICC%20World%20Cup%202023%20at%20the%20halfway%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Rohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20is%20batting%20with%20the%20highest%20strike-rate%20among%20all%20openers%20in%20the%20tournament.%20The%20Indian%20skipper%20amassed%20311%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2062.20%20and%20a%20magnificent%20strike-rate%20of%20133.47.%20His%20tally%20includes%20one%20blazing%20century%20against%20Afghanistan%20and%20a%20half-century%20against%20Pakistan.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20also%20has%20the%20most%20sixes%20in%20the%20tournament%20so%20far%2C%20with%2017%20of%20his%20hits%20going%20out%20of%20the%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20contender%20for%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Tournament%20award%2C%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%20is%20batting%20like%20a%20dream%20at%20the%20ICC%20World%20Cup%202023.%20De%20Kock%2C%20who%20is%20set%20to%20retire%20from%20ODIs%20after%20this%20tournament%2C%20has%20already%20smashed%20three%20centuries%20and%20has%20accumulated%20407%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2081.40%20and%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20114.97.%20His%20three%20centuries%20so%20far%20have%20come%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Australia%20and%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Virat%20Kohli%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%2C%20often%20hailed%20as%20the%20king%20of%20run%20chases%2C%20is%20living%20up%20to%20that%20prestigious%20title%20in%20the%20ongoing%20tournament.%20With%20354%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%2C%20he%20is%20second%20only%20to%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%20in%20the%20run-scoring%20charts.%20Kohli%20is%20averaging%20a%20staggering%20118%20so%20far%20and%20is%20batting%20at%20a%20strike-rate%20of%2090.53.%20In%20the%20five%20matches%2C%20he%20has%20scored%20one%20century%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20three%20half-centuries%2C%20missing%20out%20on%20a%2050%2B%20score%20only%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Pakistan%20have%20had%20a%20disappointing%20tournament%20so%20far%2C%20Mohammad%20Rizwan's%20exploits%20with%20the%20bat%20have%20been%20a%20redeeming%20feature.%20With%20302%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2075.50%2C%20Rizwan%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20five%20run-scorers%20in%20the%20tournament.%20The%20highlight%20of%20his%20campaign%20has%20been%20the%20match-winning%20century%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20which%20saw%20Pakistan%20complete%20the%20biggest%20chase%20in%20World%20Cup%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Daryll%20Mitchell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand's%20Daryll%20Mitchell%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20underrated%20players%20in%20the%20tournament%20right%20now.%20The%2032-year-old%20batter%20is%20making%20a%20stellar%20contribution%20to%20the%20Kiwis%20with%20his%20power-hitting%20in%20the%20middle%20order%2C%20scoring%20268%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20until%20now.%20He%20averages%20a%20whopping%2089.33%20at%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20108.06.%20He%20made%20one%20terrific%20century%20against%20India%20and%20smashed%20a%2067-ball%2089%20against%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Heinrich%20Klaasen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20strikers%20in%20world%20cricket%20right%20now%2C%20Heinrich%20Klaasen%20is%20lighting%20up%20the%20World%20Cup%20with%20his%20power-hitting.%20The%20South%20African%20batter%20is%20in%20the%20form%20of%20his%20life%20and%20has%20scored%20288%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20so%20far.%20His%20strike-rate%20of%20150.79%20is%20the%20best%20in%20the%20tournament%20(minimum%2050%20runs)%20and%20his%20tally%20includes%20one%20century%20and%20one%20half-century.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Marco%20Jansen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMarco%20Jansen%20has%20established%20himself%20as%20a%20trustworthy%20all-rounder%20in%20this%20tournament.%20The%20tall%20lanky%20fast%20bowler%20has%20been%20among%20the%20wickets%20regularly%2C%20scalping%2010%20in%20five%20matches%20so%20far.%20However%2C%20his%20123-run%20contribution%20at%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20126.80%20has%20added%20great%20depth%20to%20South%20Africa's%20batting%2C%20making%20him%20a%20lethal%20finisher%20for%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Mitchell%20Santner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20many%20would've%20expected%20Mitchell%20Santner%20to%20make%20his%20case%20as%20the%20leading%20wicket-taker%20in%20the%20tournament%20at%20the%20halfway%20stage.%20But%20after%20match%20No.%2023%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Kiwi%20left-arm%20spinner%20who%20takes%20the%20top%20spot%20with%2012%20wickets%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2016.91%20and%20an%20economy%20of%204.25.%20Santner%20has%20also%20scored%2044%20runs%20with%20the%20bat%20at%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20183.33.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%20Adam%20Zampa%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20poor%20start%20to%20the%20tournament%2C%20Adam%20Zampa%20has%20slowly%20stamped%20his%20authority%20on%20the%20pitches%20that%20offer%20great%20help%20to%20spinners.%20The%20Australian%20leggie%20has%20picked%20up%20nine%20wickets%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2024.78%20and%20maintains%20an%20economy%20of%206.19.%20Zampa's%20spells%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20(4%2F47)%20and%20Pakistan%20(4%2F53)%20were%20crucial%20in%20the%20five-time%20champions'%20resurgence%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E10.%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPossibly%20the%20best%20fast%20bowler%20in%20the%20tournament%20right%20now%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20lethal%20and%20economical%20spells%20have%20given%20India%20a%20great%20edge%20in%20the%20five%20matches%20so%20far.%20Bumrah%20picked%20up%2011%20wickets%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2016.27%20and%20his%20economy%20of%203.81%20is%20the%20best%20among%20all%20bowlers%20who%20bowled%2010%20overs%20or%20more.%20Bumrah%20was%20named%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20where%20he%20returned%20with%20figures%20of%202%2F19.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E11.%20Matt%20Henry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMatt%20Henry%20is%20making%20great%20use%20of%20the%20Indian%20conditions%2C%20although%20they%20are%20not%20the%20friendliest%20for%20fast%20bowlers.%20The%20Kiwi%20speedster%20has%2010%20wickets%20to%20his%20credit%20in%20five%20matches%2C%20at%20an%20average%20of%2021.70%20and%20a%20splendid%20economy%20of%205.10.%20His%20best%20figures%20in%20the%20tournament%20came%20against%20Netherlands%20(3%2F40)%20and%20England%20(3%2F48)%2C%20where%20he%20picked%20up%20some%20prized%20scalps%20and%20saw%20his%20team%20through%20to%20a%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698392640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fpfoqp7sg_rohit-sharma-_625x300_23_