ttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16115416%2Frupee-g803a66102_1920.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20outstanding%20amount%20due%20from%20wilful%20defaulters%20has%20risen%20at%20a%20pace%20of%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore%20daily%20since%20March%202019%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fdues-from-wilful-defaulters-rose-by-rs-100-cr-per-day-since-covid-19-struck-123102700166_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20the%20amount%20due%20from%20wilful%20defaulters%20has%20risen%20by%20at%20least%20Rs%201.2%20trillion%20%E2%80%93%20or%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20amount%20due%20has%20risen%20more%20than%2050%25%20to%20Rs%203%20trillion%20as%20of%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20wilful%20defaulter%20is%20a%20specific%20term%20used%20for%20borrowers%20who%2C%20despite%20having%20the%20ability%20to%20do%20so%2C%20do%20not%20pay%20back%20a%20loan.%20It%20does%20not%20refer%20to%20small%20borrowers%20like%20a%20farmer%20in%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20massive%20rise%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20a%20day%20since%20March%202019%20severely%20dents%20the%20claim%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20July%2022%20that%20the%20previous%20UPA%20government%20had%20%E2%80%9Cdestroyed%E2%80%9D%20the%20banking%20sector%20with%20%E2%80%9Cscams%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20his%20dispensation%20has%20restored%20its%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20financial%20health%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fpublic-sector-banks-earlier-known-for-huge-losses-npas-now-for-record-profits-pm-modi%2Farticle67108908.ece%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fpublic-sector-banks-earlier-known-for-huge-losses-npas-now-for-record-profits-pm-modi%2Farticle67108908.ece%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1698476832980000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1Xx1pCoOScorBSW0uJn5go%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20is%20based%20on%20data%20from%20TransUnion%20CIBIL.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20is%20updated%20by%20various%20financial%20institutions%20with%20varying%20frequency.%20The%20figures%20reflect%20the%20latest%20available%20numbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20the%20newspaper%2C%20It%20cautions%20that%20this%20might%20be%20an%20underestimate.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20amount%20may%20be%20larger%20since%20at%20least%20one%20nationalised%20bank%20and%20one%20private%20sector%20bank%20have%20not%20reported%20June%20numbers%20yet.%20The%20overall%20amount%20has%20remained%20over%20the%20Rs%203%20trillion%20mark%20for%20at%20least%20four%20quarters%20in%20a%20row%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20recently%20proposed%20that%20wilful%20defaulters%20must%20be%20declared%20as%20such%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fwilful-defaulter-must-be-identified-within-six-months-after-npa-tag-123092101223_1.html%5C%22%3Ewithin%20six%20months%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20loan%20becoming%20a%20non-performing%20asset%20(NPA).%20The%20central%20bank%20has%20asked%20for%20public%20comments%20on%20the%20proposal%20by%20October-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrivate%20sector%20banks%20and%20other%20financial%20institutions%20have%20seen%20a%20small%20increase%20in%20their%20share%20of%20such%20loans%20(which%20are%20not%20being%20returned)%2C%20but%20public%20banks%2C%20worryingly%2C%20account%20for%20the%20largest%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20share%20in%20money%20owed%20by%20wilful%20defaulters%20was%2077.5%25%20in%20June%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWilful%20defaulters%20owe%20ten%20nationalised%20banks%20another%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20crore%2C%20of%20which%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20is%20owed%20Rs%2080%2C000%20crore%20as%20of%20June.%20The%20private%20sector%20banks%E2%80%99%20outstanding%20amount%20is%20Rs%2053%2C500%20crore%20in%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Suit%20Boot%20ki%20Sarkar%E2%80%99%20and%20charges%20of%20cronyism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20has%20been%20under%20pressure%20since%20RTI%20replies%2C%20parliamentary%20questions%20and%20bank%20data%20have%20revealed%20the%20massive%20amounts%20of%20public%20money%20owed%20by%20big%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20worsening%20performance%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Finternational%2F2023%2F05%2F02%2Fthe-2023-crony-capitalism-index%5C%22%3ECrony%20Capitalism%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20added%20grist%20to%20the%20Opposition%20campaign%20of%20%E2%80%98suit-boot%20ki%20sarkar%E2%80%99%2C%20shorthand%20for%20a%20government%20for%20cronies%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZ0uioKWABqo%5C%22%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20popularised%20after%20the%20Modi%20government%20presented%20the%20controversial%20Land%20Bill%20in%202015%20that%20it%20was%20forced%20to%20withdraw.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20ranks%20at%20number%2010%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98crony%20capitalism%E2%80%99%20index.%20Since%202013%2C%20wealth%20from%20%E2%80%9Ccrony-capitalist%20sectors%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%20rose%20from%205%25%20to%208%25%20of%20its%20GDP%20as%20per%20the%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fbanks-lost-rs-10-lakh-crore-in-5-years-mehul-choksi-top-debtor-418178%5C%22%3Ewritten%20reply%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20finance%20Bhagwat%20Karad%20in%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20monsoon%20session%20created%20a%20furore%20when%20he%20revealed%20that%20scheduled%20commercial%20banks%20%E2%80%9Chave%20written%20off%20an%20aggregate%20amount%20of%20Rs%2010%2C57%2C326%20crore%20during%20the%20last%20five%20financial%20years%20(RBI%20provisional%20data%20for%20FY%202022-23).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20top%20ten%20wilful%20defaulters%20owe%20Rs%2040%2C825%20crore%20to%20scheduled%20commercial%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20top%2050%20loan%20defaulters%20owe%20Rs%2087%2C295%20crore%20to%20banks%20and%20financial%20institutions%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry.%20Fugitive%20Mehul%20Choksi%E2%80%99s%20Gitanjali%20Gems%20is%20the%20biggest%20wilful%20defaulter%2C%20owing%20Rs%208%2C738%20crore%20to%20banks%2C%20followed%20by%20Era%20Infra%20Engineering%20Limited%20owing%20Rs%205%2C750%20crore%2C%20REI%20Agro%20Limited%20Rs%205%2C148%20crore%2C%20ABG%20Shipyard%20Limited%20Rs%204%2C774%20crore%2C%20and%20Concast%20Steel%20and%20Power%20Limited%20Rs%203%2C911%20crore.%20Wilful%20default%20cases%20have%20been%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20as%20banks%20have%20filed%20suits%20against%2036%2C150%20NPA%20accounts%20to%20recover%20Rs%209.26%20lakh%20crore%20in%20FY23%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Feconomy%2Fstory%2Fwilful-default-cases-on-the-rise-banks-filed-suits-against-36150-npa-accounts-to-recover-rs-926-lakh-cr-in-fy23-402252-2023-10-17%5C%22%3Ea%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20of%20public%20money%20with%20this%20government%20has%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20earlier%20too%2C%20when%20a%20controversy%20broke%20over%20the%20Adani%20Group%20after%20a%20report%20released%20by%20Hindenburg%20Research%20revealed%20alleged%20irregularities.%20Charges%20were%20made%20of%20LIC%20being%20asked%20to%20buy%20into%20Adani%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcongress-questions-lics-increase