ing%20on%20a%20podcast%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-suggests-70-hour-work-week-to-youngsters-sparks-debate-4516739%5C%22%3EMr%20Narayana%20Murthy%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20India's%20work%20productivity%20is%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world%20and%20asked%20the%20youth%20the%20contribute%20towards%20building%20the%20culture%20so%20that%20India%20can%20compete%20effectively%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20He%20also%20drew%20parallels%20with%20Japan%20and%20Germany%2C%20two%20countries%20that%20implemented%20the%20extended%20working%20hours%20after%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%20But%20he%20is%20not%20the%20first%20corporate%20leader%20to%20have%20suggested%20a%20similar%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbhash%2Fstatus%2F1717517238650188068%5C%22%3EBhavish%20Aggarwal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Ola%2C%20endorsed%20Mr%20Narayana%20Murthy's%20advice%2C%20saying%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bour%20moment%20to%20go%20all%20in%20and%20build%20in%201%20generation%20what%20other%20countries%20have%20built%20over%20many%20generations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Narayana%20Murthy%20had%20made%20a%20similar%20call%20for%20professionals%20to%20work%20long%20hours%20in%202020%2C%20when%20he%20said%20that%20Indians%20should%20work%2060%20hours%20a%20week%20for%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20years%20to%20revive%20the%20post-pandemic%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F04%2F15%2Fbusiness%2Fjack-ma-996-china%2Findex.html%5C%22%3EJack%20Ma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20founded%20Alibaba%2C%20endorsed%20the%20controversial%20%26quot%3B996%26quot%3B%20rule%20in%20China's%20tech%20industry%2C%20saying%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20that%20employees%20who%20worked%20longer%20hours%20will%20get%20the%20%26quot%3Brewards%20of%20hard%20work%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20refers%20to%20working%20from%209%20am%20to%209%20pm%20six%20days%20a%20week%20and%20is%20said%20to%20be%20common%20among%20the%20country's%20big%20technology%20companies%20and%20start-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur's%20comments%20prompted%20criticism%20from%20Chinese%20social%20media%20users.%20They%20said%20the%20controversial%20rule%20will%20affect%20the%20family%20life%2C%20and%20no%20one%20will%20have%20children%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20world's%20richest%20man%20and%20CEO%20of%20many%20companies%2C%20had%20asked%20the%20staff%20at%20Twitter%2C%20which%20he%20acquired%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20to%20work%20for%20more%20than%20100%20hours%20in%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2022%2Fnov%2F16%2Felon-musk-gives-twitter-staff-deadline-to-commit-to-being-hardcore%5C%22%3EMr%20Musk%20sent%20an%20email%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20staff%20in%20which%20he%20said%20that%20Twitter%20%26quot%3Bwill%20need%20to%20be%20extremely%20hardcore%26quot%3B%20in%20order%20to%20succeed%2C%20reported%20The%20Guardian.%20Outlining%20his%20work%20day%2C%20the%20Twitter%20owner%20said%20he%20sometimes%20sleeps%20in%20the%20office%20and%20expected%20the%20staff%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Shantanu%20Deshpande%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Bombay%20Shaving%20Company%2C%20had%20said%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20that%20freshers%20should%20work%2018%20hours%20per%20day.%20%26quot%3BEat%20well%20and%20stay%20fit%2C%20but%20put%20in%20the%2018-hour%20days%20for%20at%20least%204-5%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20done%20by%20Harvard%20Business%20Review%20in%202018%20said%20that%20CEOs%20in%20the%20US%20work%209.7%20hours%20per%20weekday%2C%20and%20another%203.9%20hours%20per%20weekend%20day.%20They%20also%20put%20in%20extra%20work%20during%20the%20weekend%20and%20vacations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20survey%20of%20357%20Indian%20CEOs%20of%20listed%20Indian%20manufacturing%20firms%20by%20economic%20research%20outfit%20International%20Growth%20Centre%20revealed%20that%20the%20average%20Indian%20CEO%20works%2039%20hours%20a%20week.%20This%20meant%20most%20bosses%20are%20on%20the%20job%20for%20close%20to%208-9%20hours%20a%20weekday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698384840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-04%2Fnarayana-murthy-650-400_650x400_61491204559.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-pitches-for-70-hour-work-week-what-global-ceos-have-said-4518240%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%2C%20world's%20richest%20man%20and%20CEO%20of%20many%20companies%2C%20had%20asked%20the%20staff%20at%20Twitter%2C%20which%20he%20acquired%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20to%20work%20for%20more%20than%20100%20hours%20in%20a%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-pitches-for-70-hour-work-week-what-global-ceos-have-said-4518240%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-pitches-for-70-hour-work-week-what-global-ceos-have-said-4518240%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-pitches-for-70-hour-work-week-what-global-ceos-have-said-4518240%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Comedian%20Hasan%20Minhaj%20Said%20On%20Allegations%20Of%20Faking%20Islamophobia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EComedian%20Hasan%20Minhaj%20was%20accused%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Yorker%20%3C%2Fem%3Emagazine%20story%20of%20fabricating%20or%20exaggerating%20the%20personal%20stories%20he%20tells%20in%20his%20stand-up%20routine.%20The%20article%20suggested%20that%20he%20was%20not%20truthful%20in%20his%20accounts%20of%20his%20life%20experiences%2C%20particularly%20those%20related%