bombing%20campaign%20--%20said%20Israel%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Braining%20down%20hellfire%20on%20Hamas%26quot%3B%20and%20killing%20%26quot%3Bthousands%20of%20terrorists%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20his%20war%20cabinet%20and%20the%20military%20would%20determine%20the%20timing%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bground%20offensive%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20goal%20to%20%26quot%3Beliminate%20Hamas%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbring%20our%20captives%20home%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas'%C2%A0armed%20wing%20said%20Israeli%20strikes%20have%20killed%20almost%2050%20of%20the%20222%C2%A0hostages%20its%20operatives%20seized%20during%20the%C2%A0attacks.%C2%A0Hamas%20has%20released%20four%20hostages%20so%20far.%20The%20Palestinian%20group%20released%20two%20elderly%20Isreli%20women%20on%20Monday%20citing%20%26quot%3Bcompelling%20humanitarian%26quot%3B%20reasons%2C%20after%20mediation%20by%20Qatar%20and%20Egypt.%20Their%20release%20comes%20days%20after%20a%20US%20mother%20and%20daughter%20were%20freed.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20military%20struck%20two%20facilities%20in%20eastern%20Syria%20used%20by%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC)%20and%20affiliated%20groups%20today.%C2%A0The%20strikes%20in%20Syria%20follow%20a%20direct%20warning%20from%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20Iran's%20supreme%20leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20against%20the%20strikes%20on%20US%20troops.%20Defense%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%2C%20however%2C%20%C2%A0sought%20to%20distance%20the%20Syria%20strikes%20from%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20militants%20in%20Gaza.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EUS%20forces%20have%20been%20attacked%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20times%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%20in%20the%20past%20week%20by%20what%20Washington%20suspects%20are%20Iran-backed%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ESince%20then%2C%20Gaza's%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20says%20more%20than%207%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20Israel's%20relentless%