n.%20That%20they%20are%20now%20saying%20only%20Bharat%20should%20be%20used%20as%20a%20country%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20a%20narrow%20politics.%20Kerala%20cannot%20accept%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20termed%20it%20another%20move%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20Union%20government%20to%20distort%20historical%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20after%20NCERT%20had%20removed%20certain%20portions%2C%20we%20included%20them%20in%20the%20syllabus%20taught%20in%20the%20state%20through%20additional%20textbooks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEducation%20was%20a%20state%20subject%20before%20being%20put%20in%20the%20concurrent%20list%2C%20in%20the%20Seventh%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20But%20school%20education%20is%20still%20an%20area%20with%20considerable%20say%20of%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProfessor%20C.I.%20Issac%2C%20head%20of%20the%20sub-committee%20at%20NCERT%20whose%20recommendation%20that%20India%20be%20renamed%20Bharat%20has%20stirred%20up%20a%20controversy%2C%20while%20reacting%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20NCERT%20had%20not%20included%20his%20committee%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20NCERT%20is%20nowadays%20led%20by%20%E2%80%9CJNU%20products%2C%20who%20have%20preconceptions%20about%20everything%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20bureaucracy%20nowadays.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20225px)%2085vw%2C%20225px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27092418%2Fdownload.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22225%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27092418%2Fdownload.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27092418%2Fdownload-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681967%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22225%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EC.I.%20Issac.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40prof_issac%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIssac%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20seven-member%20committee%20unanimously%20agreed%20on%20it.%20One%20member%20was%20from%20NCERT%20and%20he%20did%20not%20object%20either%20in%20any%20of%20the%20three%20or%20four%20meetings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20surprise%20that%20the%20recommendations%20did%20not%20make%20their%20way%20into%20the%20final%20report.%20%E2%80%9COur%20recommendation%20was%20not%20added%20in%20the%20final%20copy%20and%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20minister.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20minister.%20It%20is%20not%20my%20responsibility.%20Minister%20never%20called%20us%2C%20never%20cross%20verified.%20Whatever%20was%20given%2C%20he%20signed%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackdrop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20opposition%20group%20has%20been%20using%20the%20acronym%20INDIA%2C%20Modi%20personally%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20been%20visibly%20unsettled%20and%20led%20a%20controversial%20campaign%20to%20minimise%20the%20use%20of%20the%20name%20of%20the%20country.%20An%20invitation%20from%20the%20President%20of%20India%20for%20a%20dinner%20during%20the%20G-20%20introduced%20the%20Government%20of%20Bharat%20to%20the%20exclusion%20of%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpresident-of-bharat-g20-invitation%5C%22%3Eattracting%20comments%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20deep%20insecurity%20INDIA%20had%20bred%20in%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArticle%201%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%2C%20that%20is%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20both%20terms%20used%20interchangeably%20and%20effortlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20struggling%20to%20rename%20NDA%20(adding%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98Development%E2%80%99%2C%20instead%20of%20Democratic).%20He%20also%20referred%20to%20proscribed%20groups%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fnews%2Fpm-modi-takes-a-jibe-oppositions-india-alliance-says-attempt-to-mislead-people-as-11690266305090.html%5C%22%3E%2C%20the%20Indian%20Mujahideen%20and%20PFI%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20dubious%20case%20that%20all%20things%20with%20India%20in%20their%20name%2C%20weren%E2%80%99t%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Rhetoric%2C%20Routine%20and%20Ruse%20of%20a%20Regime%3A%20The%20Case%20of%20NCERT%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fthe-rhetoric-routine-and-ruse-of-a-regime-the-case-of-ncert%5C%22%3EThe%20Rhetoric%2C%20Routine%20and%20Ruse%20of%20a%20Regime%3A%20The%20Case%20of%20NCERT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20RSS%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIssac%20has%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bhartiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20RSS%2C%20I%20am%20a%20church%20going%20Christian.%20Who%20told%20you%20I%20am%20RSS.%20I%20am%20non-Brahmin.%20Mine%20is%20a%20500-year-old%20Christian%20family.%20I%20have%20noting%20to%20do%20with%20RSS.%20Please%20don%E2%80%99t%20bring%20in%20RSS.%20They%20do%20not%20decide%20these%20things.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIssac%20says%20the%20change%20in%20name%20should%20be%20taught%20from%20Classes%207%20to%2012.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CUp%20to%20Class%207%2C%20the%20local%20body%20school%20can%20decide%20what%20name%20they%20want%20to%20call%20India%20by.%20They%20can%20call%20whatever%20they%20want%20but%20from%20Class%207%20onwards%20and%20up%20to%20Class%20122%2C%20they%20have%20to%20call%20it%20Bharat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20the%20phone%20from%20Sharjah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20doing%20this%20in%20the%20public%20interest%20and%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20nation%20for%20our%20future%20generations.%20The%20name%20India%20was%20used%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%201868%20when%20the%20East%20India%20company%20administration%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20Crown.%20But%20the%20name%20Bharat%20has%20been%20used%20for%207%2C000%20years.%20Kalidasa%20used%20it%2C%20Tagore%20used%20it%20in%20the%20Jana%20Gana%20Mana.%20Till%20now%20there%20has%20been%20no%20controversy.%20Names%20keep%20changing.%20They%20changed%20the%20name%20of%20Bombay%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20Allahabad%20to%20Pragyaraj%2C%20only%20now%20controversy%20is%20starting.%20I%20am%20an%20academician%20and%20I%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20politics.%20It%20was%20because%20of%20my%20record%20at%20ICHR%20that%20I%20was%20appointed%20to%20this%20committee%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20my%20ancestors%20were%20Hindus.%20But%20they%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20500%20years%20ago.%20They%20had%20Hindu%20names%20but%20now%20I%20have%20Christian%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESharp%20criticism%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20change%20drew%20a%20flurry%20of%20protests%20across%20political%20parties%20on%20Thursday%2C%20with%20members%20of%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20standing%20committee%20on%20education%20saying%20they%20would%20take%20this%20up%20at%20the%20next%20meeting.%20CPI(M)%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Bikash%20Ranjan%20Bhattacharya%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20recommendations%20damage%20Indian%20unity.%20This%20name%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20given%20by%20the%20British%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20wrong%20perception%20and%20this%20has%20already%20been%20discussed%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20The%20name%20Bharat%20can%20at%20best%20be%20called%20a%20nick%20name.%20It%20arises%20from%20one%20creed%2C%20one%20feudal%20culture.%20The%20name%20India%20represents%20a%20modern%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20ex-member%20had%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20changes%20being%20made%20to%20the%20NCERT%20curriculum%20en%20masse%20and%20had%20written%20to%20chairman%20Vivek%20Thakur%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20history%20cannot%20be%20changed%20and%20attempts%20to%20do%20so%20through%20the%20back%20door%20must%20be%20scrutinised.%20The%20member%20had%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20attempt%20to%20change%20history%20must%20stand%20the%20test%20of%20objectivity%20and%20deep%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22For%20the%20BJP%2C%20Rewriting%20History%20Is%20Part%20of%20a%20Toolkit%20To%20Brighten%20Its%20Political%20Fortunes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fbjp-ncert-rewriting-history-india%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20Rewriting%20History%20Is%20Part%20of%20a%20Toolkit%20To%20Brighten%20Its%20Political%20Fortunes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENext%20steps%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENCERT%20chief%20Dinesh%20Saklani%20was%20not%20available%20for%20a%20comment.%20Another%20committee%20member%2C%20Mamata%20Yadav%2C%20who%20teaches%20at%20a%20school%20in%20Haryana%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20given%20a%20report%20as%20we%20were%20asked%20to%20give%20it.%20We%20cannot%20give%20a%20comment%20on%20what%20will%20happen%20next.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20has%20consulted%20%E2%80%9Ca%20number%20of%20academicians%E2%80%9D%2C%20Issac%20said%2C%20without%20specifying%20any%20names.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20the%20controversy%20is.%20Look%20at%20my%20family.%20We%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20but%20retain%20our%20Hindu%20value%20system%20and%20Christian%20faith.%20I%20have%20a%20Hindu%20name%20along%20with%20my%20Christian%20name.%20It%20is%20Raju.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Issac%20pushed%20back%20at%20a%20mild%20question%20of%20considering%20%E2%80%98going%20back%E2%80%99%20to%20his%20own%20name%2C%20Raju%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20I%20do%20that%3F%20In%20Hinduism%20we%20say%2C%20%3Cem%3Esarva%20deva%20namaskaram%3C%2Fem%3E.%20All%20gods%20are%20equal.%20No%20difference%20between%20Hindu%20God%20and%20Christian%20God.%20That%20is%20why%20I%20am%20still%20retaining%20my%20Christian%20faith.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-govt-rejects-ncerts-proposal-to-rename-india-as-bharat-in-school-textbooks-101698326430918.html%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20we%20saying%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20and%20Indian%20Foreign%20Service%3F%20In%20our%20passports%2C%20we%20have%20the%20Republic%20of%20India%E2%80%A6%20Why%20are%20they%20confusing%20the%20minds%20of%20Indians%3F%E2%80%A6%20Whatever%20stand%20they%20have%20taken%20is%20completely%20anti-people%2C%20anti-India%2C%20and%20anti-Bharat%E2%80%A6%20I%20am%20telling%20you%20they%20(NCERT)%20have%20been%20forced%20by%20the%20NDA%20government.%20This%20is%20completely%20wrong%E2%80%A6%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20change%20the%20history%20of%20India%E2%80%A6%20Karnataka%20will%20continue%20with%20whatever%20there%20was%20earlier%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKerala%20chief%20minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20has%20said%20that%20the%20proposal%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onmanorama.com%2Fnews%2Fkerala%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2Fchief-minister-pinarayi-vijayan-slams-ncert-panel-proposal-to-rename-india-as-bharat-in-school-textbooks.html%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.onmanorama.com%2Fnews%2Fkerala%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2Fchief-minister-pinarayi-vijayan-slams-ncert-panel-proposal-to-rename-india-as-bharat-in-school-textbooks.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D16984645288