tional%20Security%20Adviser%20Shivshankar%20Menon%20while%20delivering%20a%20keynote%20address%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20India%20International%20Centre%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20the%20launch%20of%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Security%20Challenges%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20edited%20by%20N.N.%20Vohra%2C%20made%20the%20vital%20point%20that%20the%20weakening%20of%20the%20internal%20security%20of%20India%20would%20have%20huge%20implications%20for%20national%20security%2C%20which%20is%20understood%20not%20just%20from%20the%20perspectives%20of%20physical%20or%20military%20security%20but%20also%20from%20the%20perspectives%20of%20multiple%20factors%20which%20include%20the%20economic%20security%20of%20people%2C%20human%20rights%20and%20climate%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20should%20have%20said%20very%20unequivocally%20that%20the%20processes%20of%20majoritarianism%20and%20polarisation%20triggered%20by%20the%20ruling%20regime%20of%20India%20with%20the%20aggressive%20employment%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%20binaries%2C%20amid%20calls%20for%20genocide%20and%20the%20comprehensive%20social%20and%20economic%20boycott%20of%20Muslims%20by%20several%20Hindutva%20leaders%2C%20pose%20a%20grave%20threat%20to%20internal%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20a%20BJP%20spokesperson%20said%20something%20offensive%20about%20Prophet%20Muhammad%20and%20there%20were%20sharp%20reactions%20against%20India%20from%20the%20Gulf%20countries%2C%20where%20even%20Indian%20products%20were%20boycotted.%20Even%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20reckless%20retaliatory%20response%20%E2%80%93%20killing%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20triggered%20a%20venomous%20vilification%20campaign%20against%20Muslims%20in%20India.%20Such%20incidents%20pose%20a%20huge%20challenge%20to%20internal%20security%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20would%20adversely%20affect%20national%20security.%20Menon%20broadly%20flagged%20the%20point%20that%20the%20weakening%20of%20internal%20security%20would%20weaken%20national%20security.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%20know%20that%20conscious%20attempts%20are%20being%20made%20by%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20to%20deepen%20communal%20division%20and%20caste%20discriminations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20context%20instructive%20to%20recall%20the%20illuminating%20article%20%E2%80%98A%20Foreign%20Policy%20for%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20written%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20in%201927%2C%20when%20he%20attended%20the%20League%20against%20Imperialism%E2%80%99s%20conference%20in%20Brussels.%20While%20acknowledging%20that%20some%20might%20consider%20it%20foolish%20to%20think%20of%20a%20foreign%20policy%20for%20India%20when%20British%20rule%20was%20continuing%2C%20he%20examined%20three%20problems%20while%20reflecting%20very%20presciently%20on%20how%20our%20country%20would%20forge%20relations%20with%20neighbours%20and%20the%20wider%20world.%20Presciently%2C%20he%20stated%20that%20the%20Hindu-Muslim%20question%2C%20the%20Brahmin-Non-Brahmin%20issue%20and%20our%20economic%20structure%20would%20enable%20us%20to%20conjure%20up%20a%20foreign%20policy%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20instructive%20to%20note%20that%20in%201927%2C%20he%20wrote%20that%20forces%20of%20reaction%20not%20only%20shaped%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20British%20regime%20vis-a-vis%20the%20Indian%20people%20but%20also%20affected%20Europe%20and%20the%20US.%20Very%20prophetic%20words%20for%20the%2021st%C2%A0century%2C%20which%20is%20witnessing%20an%20upsurge%20of%20right%20wing%20parties%20representing%20reactionary%20tendencies%2C%20which%20drive%20divisive%20policies%20domestically.%20In%20the%20article%2C%20Nehru%20wrote%20about%20how%20India%2C%20known%20for%20religious%20tolerance%2C%20got%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20whirlpool%20of%20religious%20division%2C%20and%20he%20urged%20examination%20to%20see%20if%20those%20divisions%20were%20determined%20by%20economic%20factors%20or%20rivalry%20based%20on%20competing%20religiosity%20and%20superstitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%20if%20a%20narrow%20outlook%2C%20religiosity%20and%20bigotry%20would%20be%20dealt%20with%20by%20cautiously%20compromising%20with%20rival%20superstitions%20and%20bigotry%2C%20or%20by%20making%20a%20frontal%20attack%20on%20it.%20Nehru%20was%20suggesting%20that%20we%20should%20take%20head%20on%20the%20forces%20representing%20and%20perpetuating%20polarisation%2C%20which%2C%20he%20thought%2C%20would%20compromise%20national%20security.%20What%20Nehru%20wrote%20in%201927%20resonates%20in%20the%20India%20of%202023%2C%20when%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20ideologically%20fight%20the%20RSS%20and%20BJP%20to%20defeat%20communal%20forces%20and%20neutralise%20the%20toxic%20bigotry%20rooted%20in%20majoritarianism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20instructive%20that%20Nehru%20also%20wrote%20about%20capitalism%20while%20reflecting%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20policy.%20He%20asked%20if%20a%20capitalist%20structure%20should%20be%20retained%2C%20or%20some%20kind%20of%20socialist%20pattern%20would%20inform%20India%E2%80%99s%20future%20constitutional%20scheme.%20Those%20ideas%20of%20Nehru%20assume%20greater%20significance%20now%20when%20concerns%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20crony%20capitalism%2C%20which%20is%20pumping%20vast%20amounts%20of%20money%20into%20India%20from%20questionable%20sources%2C%20which%20pose%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20internal%20security%20by%20exacerbating%20economic%20inequalities%20in%20our%20country.%20The%20Opposition%20is%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20funds%20being%20allegedly%20channelled%20through%20offshore%20companies%2C%20recalling%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20need%20to%20examine%20if%20a%20capitalist%20economy%20was%20endangering%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20historical%20context%20that%20Shivshankar%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20analysis%20of%20linkages%20between%20internal%20security%20and%20national%20security%20should%20be%20se