rt%20of%20Palestine%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20US%20which%20has%20reaffirmed%20support%20for%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F25%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fbiden-albanese-australia-israel.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Israel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20this%20juncture.%20Prominent%20celebrities%20have%20proven%20unflinching%20in%20their%20vote%20of%20confidence%20in%20how%20Israel%20is%20bombing%20the%20two%20million%20people%20in%20Palestine.%20And%20yet%20in%20a%20landscape%20as%20fraught%20as%20this%2C%20it%20is%20something%20of%20a%20reaffirmation%20of%20all%20that%20it%20means%20to%20be%20human%20that%20some%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20and%20visible%20support%20for%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20West%20has%20come%20from%20a%20group%20of%20Jewish%20people.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20organisation%20Jewish%20Voice%20for%20Peace%20was%20formed%20in%20the%201960s%20and%20claims%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20Jewish%20anti-Zionist%20organisation%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20supports%20the%20Palestinian%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20since%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20escalated%2C%20it%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20global%20headlines%20in%20its%20demonstrations%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20at%20spots%20significant%20to%20the%20US%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Zionist%20movement%20supports%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20Jewish%20state%20for%20Jews%20in%20Palestine.%20That%20such%20an%20idea%2C%20now%20actualised%2C%20is%20harmful%20to%20Palestinians%20and%20that%20Jewish%20people%20cannot%20profess%20ignorance%20of%20this%20is%20the%20rubric%20of%20JVP%E2%80%99s%20presence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20organisation%20has%20among%20its%20advisors%20famed%20scholars%20Judith%20Butler%2C%20Noam%20Chomsky%20and%20Naomi%20Klein.%20It%20also%20has%20rabbis%2C%20young%20women%2C%20elderly%20men%20and%20everyone%20in%20between.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3