%99m%20worried%20or%20troubled)%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20understand%20anything%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20studying%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20competition%20is%20ruthless%2C%20especially%20in%20NEET%2C%20where%20there%20are%20few%20seats%20in%20government%20medical%20colleges.%20Parents%20tell%20their%20children%20that%20we%20just%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20a%20paid%20seat%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20pressure%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Neena%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%20in%20Kota%2C%20says%20that%20parents%20need%20to%20support%20their%20children%20and%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20mental%20health.%20%E2%80%9CBrain%20is%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20body.%20Parents%20have%20to%20understand%20this%20fact%20and%20give%20issues%20of%20the%20mind%20that%20much%20importance.%20Parents%20keep%20telling%20their%20children%20about%20the%20sacrifices%20they%E2%80%99ve%20made%20and%20the%20financial%20burden%20to%20send%20them%20to%20Kota%2C%20adding%20to%20a%20teenager%E2%80%99s%20woes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20parents%2C%20the%20major%20issue%20is%20with%20the%20education%20system.%20These%20stakeholders%20say%20that%20the%20government%20must%20work%20on%20modifying%20the%20format%20of%20competitive%20exams%2C%20making%20it%20less%20rejective.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20students%2C%20they%20must%20have%20a%20Plan%20B%2C%20urges%20Thakur.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%20can%E2%80%99t%20become%20doctors%20and%20engineers.%20Some%20of%20us%20will%20be%20successful%2C%20some%20not.%20Keep%20a%20Plan%20B%20ready.%20It%E2%80%99s%20better%20than%20Plan%20A%20in%20most%20cases.%20You%E2%80%99ll%20flourish%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20worry.%20Becoming%20a%20doctor%20or%20engineer%20is%20the%20means%20to%20the%20goal%3B%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20the%20goal%20itself.%20So%20make%20friends%2C%20have%20some%20hobbies%20and%20enjoy%20your%20student%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVijayvargiya%20says%20students%20must%20learn%20that%20failures%20are%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20accept%20that%20competition%20is%20inevitable.%20Teach%20your%20children%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail.%20Put%20in%20your%20best%2C%20work%20hard%2C%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20lose%20heart%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20what%20you%20want%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331067%2Framji-swaminathan-craftizan-miniature-models-of-isro-rockets-satellites-chandrayaan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20Indians%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20achieved%20success%20after%20failing%20to%20get%20into%20the%20career%20they%20wanted.%20Dr%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20an%20aerospace%20scientist%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20former%20President%2C%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20fighter%20pilot%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20get%20through%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20by%20a%20whisker.%20He%20did%20not%20give%20up%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20India%20got%20a%20missile%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20concurs%2C%20and%20says%20that%20we%20all%20went%20through%20failures%20at%20one%20point%20in%20our%20lives%20and%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20all%20overcome%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLife%20is%20very%20big.%20You%20will%20feel%20bad%20for%20that%20moment%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20into%20an%20IIT%20or%20medical%20college.%20There%20are%20100%20more%20avenues.%20Explore%20them.%20One%20day%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20look%20back%20at%20this%20and%20laugh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20hopefully.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698069242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKOta-1-1698067807.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%