0the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20drought%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Maharashtra%20during%202013-2016%2C%20the%20worst%20to%20hit%20in%2040%20years%2C%20that%20a%20fundamental%20shift%20took%20place%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20Nutan%20Upendra%20Desai%20aka%20Nutanben%2C%20now%2051.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202016%2C%20when%20she%20found%20herself%20in%20remote%20Ambajogai%20in%20Beed%20district%20to%20oversee%20her%20team%E2%80%99s%20water%20rejuvenation%20work%2C%20she%20witnessed%20what%20she%20thought%20existed%20only%20in%20films.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20parched%20and%20cracked%20earth%2C%20the%20emaciated%20and%20undernourished%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20and%20the%20cattle%20dying%20from%20the%20lack%20of%20water%2C%20all%20changed%20her%20perspective.%20As%20if%20these%20conditions%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20she%20discovered%20that%20the%20people%20there%20were%20succumbing%20to%20water-borne%20diseases%20due%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20they%20were%20consuming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20shocked%20and%20concerned%20her%20more%20was%20that%20the%20people%20living%20there%20were%20consuming%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329441%2Fchennai-startup-bookwater-tracks-water-cans-quality-with-qr-codes-helps-access-safe-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20drinking%20water%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20ordinarily%20one%20would%20even%20be%20hesitant%20to%20touch.%20The%20dirty%2C%20fungus-filled%20green%20water%20with%20black%20molecules%20floating%20around%20was%20more%20than%20just%20a%20sore%20sight.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20basic%20human%20right%2C%20something%20millions%20of%20us%20take%20for%20granted%2C%20was%20being%20denied%20to%20these%20people%2C%20and%20she%20for%20one%2C%20could%20not%20live%20with%20the%20unfairness%20of%20it.%20The%20people%20were%20surviving%20on%20a%20rationed%20quantity%20of%20200%20litres%20of%20this%20fi